# ====================================
# KONFIGURASI EMAIL DENGAN FAILOVER
# ====================================
# Sistem ini akan otomatis beralih ke provider backup 
# jika provider utama gagal atau mencapai limit quota

# SMTP Provider Utama (Primary)
MAIL_MAILER=smtp
MAIL_HOST=smtp.example.com
MAIL_PORT=587
MAIL_USERNAME=your-email@example.com
MAIL_PASSWORD=your-password
MAIL_ENCRYPTION=tls
MAIL_FROM_ADDRESS=admin@nipnime.my.id
MAIL_FROM_NAME="NipNime"

# SMTP Provider Backup #1 - BREVO.COM (RECOMMENDED)
# Free: 300 emails/day, Profesional, Verified sender



# SMTP Provider Backup #2 - Gmail (Opsional)
MAIL_BACKUP2_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
MAIL_BACKUP2_PORT=587
MAIL_BACKUP2_USERNAME=your-gmail@gmail.com
MAIL_BACKUP2_PASSWORD=your-gmail-app-password
MAIL_BACKUP2_ENCRYPTION=tls

# ====================================
# CARA SETUP PROVIDER BACKUP
# ====================================
# 
# 1. BREVO.COM (RECOMMENDED - FREE 300 EMAILS/DAY):
#    ✅ Profesional & Reliable
#    ✅ Bisa pakai custom domain (admin@nipnime.my.id)
#    ✅ Dashboard analytics lengkap
#    
#    Cara Setup:
#    1. Daftar di https://app.brevo.com/account/register
#    2. Verifikasi email & lengkapi profil
#    3. Menu: SMTP & API > SMTP
#    4. Klik "Generate a new SMTP key"
#    5. Copy SMTP key ke MAIL_BACKUP_PASSWORD
#    6. Menu: Senders > Add a sender
#    7. Tambahkan: admin@nipnime.my.id
#    8. Verifikasi email sender (cek inbox admin@nipnime.my.id)
#    9. Done! Email akan terkirim dari admin@nipnime.my.id
#
#    Config:
#    MAIL_BACKUP_HOST=smtp-relay.brevo.com
#    MAIL_BACKUP_PORT=587
#    MAIL_BACKUP_USERNAME=email-login-brevo@example.com
#    MAIL_BACKUP_PASSWORD=smtp-key-dari-brevo
#
# 2. GMAIL (Gratis - Backup Terakhir):
#    - Aktifkan 2FA di Google Account
#    - Generate App Password: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
#    - Gunakan App Password di MAIL_BACKUP2_PASSWORD
#    - Limit: ~500 email/hari
#    ⚠️ Email akan dari Gmail, bukan custom domain
#
# 3. MAILGUN (Alternative):
#    - Daftar di https://www.mailgun.com
#    - 5,000 emails/month gratis
#    - Perlu verifikasi domain
#
# 4. SENDGRID (Alternative):
#    - Daftar di https://sendgrid.com
#    - 100 emails/day gratis
#    MAIL_BACKUP2_HOST=smtp.sendgrid.net
#    MAIL_BACKUP2_PORT=587
#    MAIL_BACKUP2_USERNAME=apikey
#    MAIL_BACKUP2_PASSWORD=your-sendgrid-api-key
#
# ====================================
# CARA KERJA FAILOVER
# ====================================
# 
# Sistem akan mencoba provider dengan urutan:
# 1. SMTP Primary (MAIL_HOST) - Provider utama kamu
# 2. SMTP Backup 1 (Brevo.com) - Failover pertama  
# 3. SMTP Backup 2 (Gmail) - Failover terakhir
#
# Jika provider pertama gagal/limit quota:
# ✅ Otomatis beralih ke Brevo (tetap dari admin@nipnime.my.id)
# ✅ Error di-log di storage/logs/laravel.log
# ✅ User tetap dapat menerima OTP
# ✅ Terlihat profesional karena sender tetap sama
#
# KEUNTUNGAN PAKAI BREVO:
# - Email tetap dari admin@nipnime.my.id (profesional)
# - Tidak masuk spam (deliverability tinggi)
# - Dashboard tracking email (open rate, click rate)
# - Gratis 300 emails/day (cukup untuk OTP)
# - Support responsive
#
# ====================================
